{"tid":1224273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"釋放學生 撤回惡法 嚴懲違法警","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T03:19:34.000Z","uid":54346,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e17a5384c8701ae824280fe2d0e2dcdd98f97547","tid":1224273,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:46:58.000Z","msg":"港共政府依家放風暫緩 但仲未完全撤回 佢隨時快手通過都得<br />\n<br />\n仲未計依幾日嘅白色恐怖 係非示威區入面恣意拘捕/恐嚇學生<br />\n<br />\n義士比人屈係暴徒 黑驚係咁無視警察守則做野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要繼續出黎 <br />\n<br />\n對抗白色恐怖 對抗政治檢控 對抗極權！</span></span>"},{"pid":"85a7b1e8be5516aba0d9fff07350a95fbdf69df6","tid":1224273,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd3573ae5edef514d70ff49440ad59378515179","tid":1224273,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"[緊急/請廣傳] 政府暫緩以退為進，星期日香港人唔出嚟將會一敗塗地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224213\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224213</a><br />\n<br />\n經過69百萬人遊行同612血腥鎮壓，政府既管治合法性已經危在旦夕，全世界都等緊機會作致命一擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家政府扮聽民意暫緩修例，目的係以退為進，買時間令善忘既香港人沖淡怒氣，同時令國際社會無機會出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果香港人因為政府暫緩而星期日唔出嚟，之後將會係連場既大規模清算同白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時候無人會再敢抗爭，惡法原封不動通過，69既百萬人遊行，612義士既犧牲將會毀於一旦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你唔想呢件事發生，就要趁全世界站係香港人一方，民氣最強既時候出黎遊行，堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場仗冇階段性勝利，一係贏，一係輸，winner takes all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港要贏，香港人星期日一定要出嚟，多你一個絕對好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n緊記目標只有一個：撤回惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家copy呢個post喺Facebook, IG, Whatsapp share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣組幫手整圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用盡你一切方法動員認識既人星期日出嚟堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df775ae4892cfc21af7dced27a653796c8d7548f","tid":1224273,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab16231376833b9de3773767b0c8dd8138f14ebe","tid":1224273,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f171e8a971ef20a38fe470d1442caedb44955008","tid":1224273,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b827a837de23300a2056aa21225992a9e26d44f6","tid":1224273,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933270f795b43521adf3ade720953a3786e2a4b2","tid":1224273,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae241932d88c6d52c67cbd0fb2dd14fb5a4b